#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Accounting</strong>: Manage revenues, taxes, and financial reports "
"from course sales."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ການບັນຊີ</strong>: ຈັດການລາຍຮັບ, ພາສີ ແລະ ລາຍງານການເງິນຈາກການຂາຍຫຼັກສູດ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Apps &amp; What They Do:</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ແອັບຯ ແລະ ໜ້າທີ່ຂອງພວກມັນ:</strong>"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Automate communications: </strong>Set up automated emails for course"
" completion reminders, certificates, or upselling new courses."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ລະບົບສື່ສານອັດຕະໂນມັດ: </strong>ຕັ້ງຄ່າອີເມລອັດຕະໂນມັດສຳລັບການແຈ້ງເຕືອນການຮຽນຈົບຫຼັກສູ"
"ດ, ໃບຢັ້ງຢືນ ຫຼື ການແນະນຳຫຼັກສູດໃໝ່."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid "<strong>Breaking Down Problems into Steps</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ການແຍກບັນຫາອອກເປັນຂັ້ນຕອນ</strong>"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Bundle your offers: </strong>Create course packages to increase "
"perceived value and average cart size.<strong/><br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຂາຍເປັນຊຸດ (Bundle): </strong>ສ້າງແພັກເກັດຫຼັກສູດເພື່ອເພີ່ມມູນຄ່າ ແລະ ຍອດຂາຍສະເລ່"
"ຍ.<strong/><br/>"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,description:elearning_platform.slide_slide_43
msgid ""
"<strong>C and C++</strong> give programmers more control over how computers "
"manage resources and are often used in systems programming or high-"
"performance applications."
msgstr ""
"<strong>C ແລະ C++</strong> ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ຜູ້ຂຽນໂປຣແກຣມຄວບຄຸມການຈັດການຊັບພະຍາກອນຂອງຄອມພິວເຕີໄດ້"
"ຫຼາຍຂຶ້ນ ແລະ ມັກຖືກນຳໃຊ້ໃນການຂຽນໂປຣແກຣມລະບົບ ຫຼື ແອັບພລິເຄຊັນທີ່ຕ້ອງການປະສິດທິພາບສູງ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_43
msgid ""
"<strong>C and C++</strong>: These languages give programmers low-level "
"control over how memory and hardware are used. That makes them perfect for "
"performance-heavy applications like video games, operating systems, and "
"embedded devices. For instance, much of Microsoft Windows and many game "
"engines are written in C++."
msgstr ""
"<strong>C ແລະ C++</strong>: ພາສາເຫຼົ່ານີ້ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ຜູ້ຂຽນໂປຣແກຣມຄວບຄຸມການເຮັດວຽກຂອງໜ່ວຍຄວາມຈ"
"ຳ ແລະ ຮາດແວໃນລະດັບຕ່ຳໄດ້. ເຮັດໃຫ້ພວກມັນເໝາະສຳລັບແອັບພລິເຄຊັນທີ່ຕ້ອງການປະສິດທິພາບສູງ ເຊັ່ນ: ວິດີໂອ"
"ເກມ, ລະບົບປະຕິບັດການ ແລະ ອຸປະກອນຝັງຕົວ (Embedded). ຕົວຢ່າງ: ລະບົບ Windows ສ່ວນໃຫຍ່ ແລະ ເ"
"ກມເອັນຈິນ (Game engines) ຫຼາຍໆອັນແມ່ນຖືກຂຽນດ້ວຍ C++."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Certifications</strong>: Issue completion certificates "
"automatically."
msgstr "<strong>ໃບຢັ້ງຢືນ</strong>: ອອກໃບຢັ້ງຢືນການຮຽນຈົບໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid "<strong>Check your logic manually</strong>:"
msgstr "<strong>ກວດສອບຕັກກະ (Logic) ຂອງທ່ານດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ</strong>:"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_51
msgid "<strong>Clean Version:</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ເວີຊັນທີ່ສະອາດ:</strong>"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Community building</strong>: Use Odoo’s Forum and Reviews features "
"to stimulate peer-to-peer support."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ການສ້າງຊຸມຊົນ</strong>: ໃຊ້ຟີເຈີເວັບບອດ (Forum) ແລະ ການຣີວິວຂອງ Odoo ເພື່ອສົ່ງເສີມກ"
"ານຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອເຊິ່ງກັນ ແລະ ກັນລະຫວ່າງຜູ້ຮຽນ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Continuous improvement</strong>: Assign responsible managers to keep"
" content evolving."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ການພັດທະນາຢ່າງຕໍ່ເນື່ອງ</strong>: ມອບໝາຍໃຫ້ຜູ້ຈັດການທີ່ຮັບຜິດຊອບເພື່ອປັບປຸງເນື້ອຫາໃຫ້ທັນສະໄ"
"ໝຢູ່ສະເໝີ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_52
msgid "<strong>Custom range</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ກຳນົດຊ່ວງຕົວເລກເອງ</strong>"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Dashboards</strong>: Monitor KPIs like course sales, student "
"engagement, or marketing performance in real time."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ແດຊບອດ (Dashboards)</strong>: ຕິດຕາມ KPI ເຊັ່ນ: ຍອດຂາຍຫຼັກສູດ, ການມີສ່ວນຮ່ວມຂອ"
"ງນັກຮຽນ ຫຼື ປະສິດທິພາບການຕະຫຼາດແບບໃຊ້ເວລາຈິງ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid "<strong>Draw it out</strong>:"
msgstr "<strong>ແຕ້ມແຜນຜັງອອກມາ</strong>:"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Engage through social media: </strong>Repurpose snippets of your "
"lessons into posts or teasers to drive traffic back to your platform."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ສ້າງສ່ວນຮ່ວມຜ່ານໂຊຊຽວມີເດຍ: </strong>ນຳເອົາບາງສ່ວນຂອງບົດຮຽນມາເຮັດເປັນໂພສ ຫຼື ຄລິບສັ້"
"ນເພື່ອດຶງດູດຄົນໃຫ້ກັບເຂົ້າມາຫາແພລດຟອມຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Engagement analytics</strong>: Measure clicks, open rates, and "
"conversions."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ການວິເຄາະການມີສ່ວນຮ່ວມ</strong>: ວັດແທກການຄລິກ, ອັດຕາການເປີດເບິ່ງ ແລະ ການປ່ຽນເປັນ"
"ລູກຄ້າ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Feedback &amp; reviews</strong>: Collect star ratings and comments."
msgstr "<strong>ຄຳຕິຊົມ ແລະ ການຣີວິວ</strong>: ເກັບກຳການໃຫ້ດາວ ແລະ ຄຳຄິດເຫັນ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Gamification</strong>: Add leaderboards, badges, and XP points for "
"learner engagement."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ການນຳໃຊ້ຮູບແບບເກມ (Gamification)</strong>: ເພີ່ມຕາຕະລາງຄະແນນ, ຫຼຽນລາງວັນ ແລ"
"ະ ຄະແນນ XP ເພື່ອສ້າງຄວາມໜ້າສົນໃຈໃຫ້ກັບຜູ້ຮຽນ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Gamify your courses: </strong>Add badges and leaderboards to "
"encourage competition and motivation."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ສ້າງເກມໃນຫຼັກສູດ: </strong>ເພີ່ມຫຼຽນລາງວັນ ແລະ ຕາຕະລາງຄະແນນເພື່ອສົ່ງເສີມການແຂ່ງຂັນ ແ"
"ລະ ສ້າງແຮງຈູງໃຈ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_43
msgid ""
"<strong>Go (Golang)</strong>: Created by Google, Go is simple, fast, and "
"great for building scalable web servers or cloud applications. It’s used in "
"backend systems that handle millions of requests per second."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Go (Golang)</strong>: ສ້າງຂຶ້ນໂດຍ Google, ພາສາ Go ມີຄວາມງ່າຍດາຍ, ໄວ ແລະ ເໝ"
"າະສຳລັບການສ້າງເວັບເຊີບເວີ ຫຼື ແອັບພລິເຄຊັນບົນຄລາວ (Cloud). ມັນຖືກນຳໃຊ້ໃນລະບົບ Backend ທີ່ຕ້ອງຮອ"
"ງຮັບການຮ້ອງຂໍຫຼາຍລ້ານຄັ້ງຕໍ່ວິນາທີ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.homepage
msgid "<strong>Guidance You Can Trust</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ຄຳແນະນຳທີ່ທ່ານໄວ້ວາງໃຈໄດ້</strong>"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_52
msgid "<strong>Guided Exercise: A Number Guessing Game</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ບົດຝຶກຫັດ: ເກມທາຍຕົວເລກ</strong>"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid "<strong>High-level problem:</strong> <em>“Make toast.”</em>"
msgstr "<strong>ບັນຫາລະດັບສູງ (ພາບລວມ):</strong> <em>“ເຮັດເຂົ້າຈີ່ປີ້ງ.”</em>"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_51
msgid ""
"<strong>Hint:</strong> Use meaningful variable names, indentation, and maybe"
" a function."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຄຳແນະນຳ:</strong> ໃຊ້ຊື່ຕົວປ່ຽນທີ່ມີຄວາມໝາຍ, ມີການຍໍ້ໜ້າ ແລະ ອາດຈະໃຊ້ຟັງຊັນ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid "<strong>Identify repeated patterns</strong>:"
msgstr "<strong>ລະບຸຮູບແບບທີ່ເຮັດຊ້ຳ</strong>:"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Internal use</strong>: Assign courses free of charge for employee "
"onboarding or training."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ການນຳໃຊ້ພາຍໃນ</strong>: ມອບໝາຍຫຼັກສູດໃຫ້ພະນັກງານໂດຍບໍ່ມີຄ່າໃຊ້ຈ່າຍ ສຳລັບການຝຶກອົບຮົມພ"
"ະນັກງານໃໝ່."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,description:elearning_platform.slide_slide_43
msgid ""
"<strong>Java</strong> is popular for large applications, Android apps, and "
"enterprise systems."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Java</strong> ເປັນທີ່ນິຍົມສຳລັບແອັບພລິເຄຊັນຂະໜາດໃຫຍ່, ແອັບ Android ແລະ ລະບົບລະດັບອົ"
"ງກອນ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_43
msgid ""
"<strong>Java</strong>: A powerful, general-purpose language that runs on "
"everything from large enterprise servers to Android phones. Its motto, "
"<em>“Write once, run anywhere”</em>, reflects how portable it is. A banking "
"system backend or an Android mobile game are often written in Java."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Java</strong>: ເປັນພາສາທີ່ມີປະສິດທິພາບສູງ ແລະ ໃຊ້ງານໄດ້ທົ່ວໄປ ເຊິ່ງສາມາດແລ່ນໄດ້ຕັ້ງແຕ່ເ"
"ຊີບເວີລະດັບອົງກອນໄປຈົນຮອດໂທລະສັບ Android. ຄຳຂວັນຂອງມັນແມ່ນ <em>“ຂຽນເທື່ອດຽວ, ແລ່ນໄດ້ທຸກບ່ອນ"
"”</em> ສະແດງໃຫ້ເຫັນເຖິງຄວາມສາມາດໃນການເຄື່ອນຍ້າຍໄດ້ງ່າຍ. ລະບົບຫຼັງບ້ານຂອງທະນາຄານ ຫຼື ເກມມືຖື "
"Android ມັກຈະຖືກຂຽນດ້ວຍ Java."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,description:elearning_platform.slide_slide_43
msgid ""
"<strong>JavaScript</strong> powers most websites, making pages interactive "
"and dynamic."
msgstr ""
"<strong>JavaScript</strong> ເປັນໂຕຂັບເຄື່ອນເວັບໄຊສ່ວນໃຫຍ່, ເຮັດໃຫ້ໜ້າເວັບມີການໂຕ້ຕອບ ແລະ ມີ"
"ການປ່ຽນແປງທີ່ຫຼາກຫຼາຍ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_43
msgid ""
"<strong>JavaScript</strong>: The language of the web. Every time you click a"
" button, scroll smoothly, or see live updates on a webpage, JavaScript is at"
" work. It runs inside your browser and powers dynamic sites like Facebook, "
"Twitter, and YouTube. For example, the code that updates a shopping cart "
"total instantly when you add an item is written in JavaScript."
msgstr ""
"<strong>JavaScript</strong>: ພາສາແຫ່ງໂລກເວັບໄຊ. ທຸກໆຄັ້ງທີ່ທ່ານຄລິກປຸ່ມ, ເລື່ອນໜ້າຈໍຢ່າງລື່ນໄຫຼ "
"ຫຼື ເຫັນການອັບເດດສົດໆບົນໜ້າເວັບ, ນັ້ນແມ່ນຜົນງານຂອງ JavaScript. ມັນເຮັດວຽກຢູ່ພາຍໃນບຣາວເຊີຂອງທ່າ"
"ນ ແລະ ຂັບເຄື່ອນເວັບໄຊດັງໆເຊັ່ນ Facebook, Twitter ແລະ YouTube. ຕົວຢ່າງ: ໂຄ້ດທີ່ອັບເດດຍອດລວມ"
"ໃນກະຕ່າສິນຄ້າທັນທີເມື່ອທ່ານເພີ່ມສິນຄ້າ ແມ່ນຖືກຂຽນດ້ວຍ JavaScript."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Knowledge</strong> &amp; <strong>Documents</strong>: Centralize your"
" internal documentation for trainers and staff."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຄັງຄວາມຮູ້</strong> &amp; <strong>ເອກະສານ</strong>: ລວບລວມເອກະສານພາຍໃນໄວ້"
"ບ່ອນດຽວກັນສຳລັບຜູ້ຝຶກອົບຮົມ ແລະ ພະນັກງານ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Leverage analytics: </strong>Track student progress to identify "
"bottlenecks and adjust course content accordingly."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ໃຊ້ປະໂຫຍດຈາກການວິເຄາະ: </strong>ຕິດຕາມຄວາມຄືບໜ້າຂອງນັກຮຽນເພື່ອລະບຸຈຸດທີ່ຕິດຂັດ ແລະ "
"ປັບປຸງເນື້ອຫາຫຼັກສູດໃຫ້ເໝາະສົມ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_52
msgid "<strong>Limit the number of attempts</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ຈຳກັດຈຳນວນຄັ້ງໃນການທາຍ</strong>"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Marketing apps</strong>: Send targeted campaigns to promote courses "
"&amp; connect and engage audiences through multiple social platforms."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ແອັບຯການຕະຫຼາດ</strong>: ສົ່ງແຄມເປນທີ່ກົງກັບກຸ່ມເປົ້າໝາຍເພື່ອໂປຣໂມດຫຼັກສູດ &amp; ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່"
"ກັບຜູ້ຮຽນຜ່ານເວທີໂຊຊຽວຕ່າງໆ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_51
msgid "<strong>Messy Version:</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ເວີຊັນທີ່ບໍ່ເປັນລະບຽບ:</strong>"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_52
msgid "<strong>Play again option</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ຕົວເລືອກຫຼິ້ນໃໝ່</strong>"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid ""
"<strong>Problem:</strong> You want to write a program that makes an ATM "
"simulate a cash withdrawal."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ບັນຫາ:</strong> ທ່ານຕ້ອງການຂຽນໂປຣແກຣມທີ່ຈຳລອງການຖອນເງິນຈາກຕູ້ ATM."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Projects</strong>: Organize course development and track future "
"content roadmaps."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ໂຄງການ</strong>: ຈັດລະບຽບການພັດທະນາຫຼັກສູດ ແລະ ຕິດຕາມແຜນການສ້າງເນື້ອຫາໃນອະນາຄົ"
"ດ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,description:elearning_platform.slide_slide_43
msgid ""
"<strong>Python</strong> is known for being beginner-friendly and widely used"
" in data science, web development, and automation."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Python</strong> ເປັນທີ່ຮູ້ຈັກກັນດີວ່າມັນເປັນມິດກັບຜູ້ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ ແລະ ຖືກນຳໃຊ້ຢ່າງກວ້າງຂວາງໃນດ້າ"
"ນວິທະຍາສາດຂໍ້ມູນ, ການພັດທະນາເວັບ ແລະ ລະບົບອັດຕະໂນມັດ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_43
msgid ""
"<strong>Python</strong>: Famous for its simplicity, Python reads almost like"
" English, making it a favorite for beginners. It’s widely used in data "
"science, artificial intelligence, web development (using frameworks like "
"Django), and automation. Example: writing a program that analyzes thousands "
"of tweets to find trending topics."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Python</strong>: ມີຊື່ສຽງໃນເລື່ອງຄວາມງ່າຍດາຍ, ພາສາ Python ອ່ານງ່າຍຄືກັນກັບພາສາອັງ"
"ກິດ ເຮັດໃຫ້ມັນເປັນທີ່ນິຍົມສຳລັບຜູ້ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ. ມັນຖືກນຳໃຊ້ຢ່າງກວ້າງຂວາງໃນດ້ານວິທະຍາສາດຂໍ້ມູນ, ປັນຍາປະດິດ "
"(AI), ການພັດທະນາເວັບ ແລະ ລະບົບອັດຕະໂນມັດ. ຕົວຢ່າງ: ການຂຽນໂປຣແກຣມວິເຄາະທະວິດ (Tweets) ຫຼ"
"າຍພັນອັນເພື່ອຫາຫົວຂໍ້ທີ່ກຳລັງເປັນກະແສ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,description:elearning_platform.slide_slide_43
msgid ""
"<strong>Ruby, Go, Swift, and others</strong> serve specialized roles across "
"industries."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Ruby, Go, Swift ແລະ ອື່ນໆ</strong> ມີບົດບາດສະເພາະທາງໃນອຸດສາຫະກຳຕ່າງໆ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_43
msgid ""
"<strong>Ruby</strong>: Known for its elegance and developer-friendly design."
" Popular in web development thanks to Ruby on Rails, it was once the "
"backbone of platforms like Airbnb and GitHub."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Ruby</strong>: ເປັນທີ່ຮູ້ຈັກໃນເລື່ອງຄວາມສວຍງາມຂອງໂຄ້ດ ແລະ ການອອກແບບທີ່ເປັນມິດກັບຜູ້ພັດ"
"ທະນາ. ມັນເປັນທີ່ນິຍົມໃນການພັດທະນາເວັບຍ້ອນມີ Ruby on Rails ແລະ ເຄີຍເປັນລະບົບຫຼັກຂອງແພລດຟອມດັງໆ"
"ເຊັ່ນ Airbnb ແລະ GitHub."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Sales reports</strong>: Monitor revenues and identify popular "
"courses."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ລາຍງານການຂາຍ</strong>: ຕິດຕາມລາຍຮັບ ແລະ ລະບຸຫຼັກສູດທີ່ໄດ້ຮັບຄວາມນິຍົມ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_52
msgid "<strong>Show the number of attempts taken</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ສະແດງຈຳນວນຄັ້ງທີ່ໄດ້ທາຍໄປ</strong>"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Social scheduling</strong>: Plan posts across multiple platforms."
msgstr "<strong>ການວາງແຜນໂຊຊຽວ</strong>: ວາງແຜນການໂພສລ່ວງໜ້າໃນຫຼາຍໆແພລດຟອມ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid "<strong>Start broad, then refine</strong>:"
msgstr "<strong>ເລີ່ມຈາກພາບກວ້າງ, ແລ້ວຄ່ອຍລົງລາຍລະອຽດ</strong>:"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Surveys</strong>: Gather learner feedback to continuously improve "
"course quality."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ການສຳຫຼວດ</strong>: ເກັບກຳຄຳຄິດເຫັນຂອງຜູ້ຮຽນເພື່ອປັບປຸງຄຸນນະພາບຫຼັກສູດຢ່າງຕໍ່ເນື່ອງ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_43
msgid ""
"<strong>Swift</strong>: Apple’s language for iOS and macOS development. If "
