msgstr ""
"<strong>ແຄມເປນອີເມລສະເພາະກຸ່ມ</strong>: ແບ່ງກຸ່ມຜູ້ຮຽນຕາມຄວາມສົນໃຈ ຫຼື ປະຫວັດການຊື້."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid "<strong>Think about inputs and outputs</strong>:"
msgstr "<strong>ຄິດກ່ຽວກັບຂໍ້ມູນຂາເຂົ້າ (Inputs) ແລະ ຜົນຮັບ (Outputs)</strong>:"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Tip </strong>: Check out Marketing Automation for content funnel "
