"<strong>Tip: </strong>Use pricelists for discounts, gifts, and promotions."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ເຄັດລັບ: </strong>ໃຊ້ລາຍການລາຄາ (Pricelists) ສຳລັບສ່ວນຫຼຸດ, ຂອງຂວັນ ແລະ ໂປຣໂມ"
"ຊັນ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Track student progression</strong>: See which modules they’ve "
"completed."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຕິດຕາມຄວາມຄືບໜ້າຂອງນັກຮຽນ</strong>: ເບິ່ງວ່າພວກເຂົາຮຽນຈົບໂມດູນໃດແດ່ແລ້ວ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Website integration</strong>: Courses are published directly on your"
" Odoo website."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ກັບເວັບໄຊ</strong>: ຫຼັກສູດຈະຖືກເຜີຍແຜ່ໂດຍກົງເທິງເວັບໄຊ Odoo ຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Website</strong>: Present your training catalog beautifully and "
