msgstr ""
"ພຽງແຕ່ຕ້ອງລະວັງ, ເມື່ອອັບໂຫຼດຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງແລ້ວ, ມັນຈະບໍ່ສາມາດລຶບອອກໄດ້ງ່າຍໆ. ແຕ່ທ່ານສາມາດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຖານຂໍ້"
"ມູນໃໝ່ໄດ້ທີ່"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_52
msgid "Keep a counter and display it at the end:"
msgstr "ນັບຈຳນວນຄັ້ງ ແລະ ສະແດງຜົນໃນຕອນທ້າຍ:"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_51
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_52
msgid "Key Takeaway"
msgstr "ສິ່ງສຳຄັນທີ່ຄວນຈື່"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.homepage
msgid ""
"Knowledge isn’t a finish line — it’s a journey. With every lesson, you grow "
"your skills, confidence, and creativity. Wherever you are in your learning "
"path, we’re here to help you take the next step.&amp;nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"ຄວາມຮູ້ບໍ່ແມ່ນເສັ້ນໄຊ — ແຕ່ມັນແມ່ນການເດີນທາງ. ໃນທຸກໆບົດຮຽນ, ທ່ານຈະໄດ້ພັດທະນາທັກສະ, ຄວາມໝັ້ນໃຈ ແລ"
"ະ ຄວາມຄິດສ້າງສັນ. ບໍ່ວ່າທ່ານຈະຢູ່ໃນຂັ້ນໃດຂອງການຮຽນຮູ້, ພວກເຮົາຢູ່ທີ່ນີ້ເພື່ອຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານກ້າວໄປສູ່ຂັ້ນຕໍ່ໄ"
"ປ.&amp;nbsp;"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.homepage
msgid "Learn by Doing"
msgstr "ຮຽນຮູ້ຜ່ານການລົງມືເຮັດ"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.homepage
msgid "Learn the essentials of soil, seeds, and care."
msgstr "ຮຽນຮູ້ພື້ນຖານກ່ຽວກັບດິນ, ແນວພັນ ແລະ ການເບິ່ງແຍງ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.ir_ui_view_3213
msgid "Learn. Build. Thrive."
msgstr "ຮຽນຮູ້. ສ້າງສັນ. ເຕີບໃຫຍ່."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.homepage
msgid ""
"Learning that leads to results. With hands-on lessons and guided support, "
"the majority of our learners successfully complete their courses and earn "
"valuable certifications."
msgstr ""
"ການຮຽນຮູ້ທີ່ນຳໄປສູ່ຜົນສຳເລັດ. ດ້ວຍບົດຮຽນແບບລົງມືເຮັດ ແລະ ການຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອຢ່າງໃກ້ຊິດ, ຜູ້ຮຽນສ່ວນໃຫຍ່ຂອງພວ"
"ກເຮົາສາມາດຮຽນຈົບຫຼັກສູດ ແລະ ໄດ້ຮັບໃບຢັ້ງຢືນທີ່ມີມູນຄ່າ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_52
msgid ""
"Let the player choose the minimum and maximum range for the secret number."
msgstr "ໃຫ້ນັກຫຼິ້ນເລືອກຊ່ວງຕ່ຳສຸດ ແລະ ສູງສຸດສຳລັບຕົວເລກລັບ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_52
msgid "Let the player only guess 5 times before the game ends."
msgstr "ໃຫ້ນັກຫຼິ້ນທາຍໄດ້ພຽງ 5 ຄັ້ງກ່ອນເກມຈະຈົບ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid "Let’s illustrate this with a simple example."
msgstr "ມາເບິ່ງຕົວຢ່າງງ່າຍໆເພື່ອໃຫ້ເຂົ້າໃຈພາບໄດ້ຊັດເຈນ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model:product.tag,name:elearning_platform.product_tag_2
msgid "Lifetime Access"
msgstr "ເຂົ້າເຖິງໄດ້ຕະຫຼອດຊີວິດ"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.homepage
msgid "Looking for a place to learn? We’ve got you covered!<br/><br/>"
msgstr "ກຳລັງຊອກຫາບ່ອນຮຽນຢູ່ບໍ່? ພວກເຮົາມີທຸກຢ່າງທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການ!<br/><br/>"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_51
msgid "Makes it easier to add new features."
msgstr "ເຮັດໃຫ້ການເພີ່ມຟີເຈີໃໝ່ໆເຮັດໄດ້ງ່າຍຂຶ້ນ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_51
msgid ""
"Makes learning and revisiting projects enjoyable instead of frustrating."
msgstr ""
"ເຮັດໃຫ້ການຮຽນຮູ້ ແລະ ການກັບມາກວດສອບໂຄງການເປັນເລື່ອງທີ່ໜ້າເພີດເພີນ ແທນທີ່ຈະເປັນເລື່ອງທີ່ໜ້າເບື່ອ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid ""
"Many problems involve loops (repeating steps) or conditions (if something "
"happens, do this)."
msgstr ""
"ຫຼາຍໆບັນຫາລວມມີການເຮັດຊ້ຳ (loops) ຫຼື ເງື່ອນໄຂ (ຖ້າເກີດສິ່ງນີ້, ໃຫ້ເຮັດແບບນັ້ນ)."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid "Mix flour, sugar, and eggs in a bowl."
msgstr "ປະສົມແປ້ງ, ນ້ຳຕານ ແລະ ໄຂ່ ລົງໃນຊາມ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model:slide.slide,name:elearning_platform.slide_slide_49
msgid "Module 5: Problem-Solving with Code"
msgstr "ໂມດູນ 5: ການແກ້ໄຂບັນຫາດ້ວຍໂຄ້ດ"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Monetize your courses by publishing them on your Odoo website’s shop. Learners can browse your catalog, purchase a course, and automatically gain access. Internal employees can be granted free access when courses are used for training\n"
"            purposes."
msgstr ""
"ສ້າງລາຍໄດ້ຈາກຫຼັກສູດຂອງທ່ານໂດຍການເຜີຍແຜ່ລົງໃນຮ້ານຄ້າເທິງເວັບໄຊ Odoo. ຜູ້ຮຽນສາມາດເລືອກເບິ່ງ, ຊື້ຫຼັກ"
"ສູດ ແລະ ເຂົ້າຮຽນໄດ້ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ. ສຳລັບພະນັກງານພາຍໃນ ສາມາດໄດ້ຮັບສິດເຂົ້າຮຽນຟຣີເມື່ອໃຊ້ໃນການຝຶກອົ"
"ບຮົມ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.ir_ui_view_3213
msgid "More info"
msgstr "ຂໍ້ມູນເພີ່ມເຕີມ"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_42
msgid ""
"Most people will infer the steps: get bread, add fillings, and serve it."
msgstr "ຄົນສ່ວນໃຫຍ່ຈະເຂົ້າໃຈຂັ້ນຕອນໄດ້ເອງ: ເອົາເຂົ້າຈີ່, ໃສ່ໄສ້ ແລະ ເສີບ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.ir_ui_view_3213
msgid "Most popular courses"
msgstr "ຫຼັກສູດທີ່ໄດ້ຮັບຄວາມນິຍົມສູງສຸດ"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.ir_ui_view_3213
msgid "My courses"
msgstr "ຫຼັກສູດຂອງຂ້ອຍ"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model:product.tag,name:elearning_platform.product_tag_4
msgid "Nature & Gardening"
msgstr "ທຳມະຊາດ ແລະ ການເຮັດສວນ"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.ir_ui_view_3213
msgid "Newest courses"
msgstr "ຫຼັກສູດໃໝ່ລ່າສຸດ"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.homepage
msgid "Next"
msgstr "ຕໍ່ໄປ"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.ir_ui_view_3213
msgid "No Course created yet."
msgstr "ຍັງບໍ່ທັນມີຫຼັກສູດໃດຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,description:elearning_platform.slide_slide_43
msgid ""
"No single language is “the best”—it depends on your goals. The good news is "
"that once you understand the fundamentals, switching between languages "
"becomes much easier."
msgstr ""
"ບໍ່ມີພາສາໃດທີ່ “ດີທີ່ສຸດ” — ມັນຂຶ້ນຢູ່ກັບເປົ້າໝາຍຂອງທ່ານ. ຂ່າວດີແມ່ນເມື່ອທ່ານເຂົ້າໃຈພື້ນຖານແລ້ວ, ການປ່ຽນໄປຮ"
"ຽນພາສາອື່ນຈະງ່າຍຂຶ້ນຫຼາຍ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid ""
"Notice how detailed these steps are. If you skipped one (like “insert the "
"bread”), the whole process would fail. Programming is exactly like this — "
"the level of precision matters."
msgstr ""
"ສັງເກດເບິ່ງວ່າຂັ້ນຕອນເຫຼົ່ານີ້ມີລາຍລະອຽດຫຼາຍສຳໃດ. ຖ້າທ່ານຂ້າມຂັ້ນຕອນໃດໜຶ່ງໄປ (ເຊັ່ນ “ໃສ່ເຂົ້າຈີ່”), ຂະບວ"
"ນການທັງໝົດກໍ່ຈະຫຼົ້ມເຫຼວ. ການຂຽນໂປຣແກຣມກໍ່ແມ່ນຄືກັນ — ຄວາມຊັດເຈນແມ່ນສິ່ງສຳຄັນ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid ""
"Notice that we’re not writing code yet—we’re just describing the steps. This"
" practice makes coding much easier later on."
msgstr ""
"ສັງເກດວ່າພວກເຮົາຍັງບໍ່ທັນໄດ້ຂຽນໂຄ້ດເທື່ອ — ພວກເຮົາພຽງແຕ່ບອກຂັ້ນຕອນເທົ່ານັ້ນ. ການຝຶກຝົນແບບນີ້ຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ກ"
"ານຂຽນໂຄ້ດໃນພາຍຫຼັງງ່າຍຂຶ້ນຫຼາຍ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_52
msgid ""
"Now it’s time to put everything you’ve learned into practice by building a "
"fun, interactive program: a <strong>number guessing game</strong>. This "
"project combines variables, input/output, operators, loops, and conditional "
"logic — giving you hands-on experience with core programming concepts."
msgstr ""
"ບາດນີ້ເຖິງເວລາທີ່ຈະນຳເອົາທຸກສິ່ງທີ່ທ່ານໄດ້ຮຽນມາໃຊ້ຕົວຈິງ ໂດຍການສ້າງໂປຣແກຣມທີ່ມ່ວນ ແລະ ມີການໂຕ້ຕອບ: "
"<strong>ເກມທາຍຕົວເລກ</strong>. ໂຄງການນີ້ລວມເອົາທັງຕົວປ່ຽນ, ຂໍ້ມູນຂາເຂົ້າ/ຂາອອກ, ເຄື່ອງໝາຍກາ"
"ນຄິດໄລ່, ລູບ ແລະ ຕັກກະແບບມີເງື່ອນໄຂ — ເພື່ອໃຫ້ທ່ານໄດ້ປະສົບການຕົວຈິງກັບແນວຄິດຫຼັກຂອງການຂຽນໂປຣແກຣ"
"ມ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid ""
"Now let’s apply this mindset to coding. Suppose we want a program that adds "
"two numbers given by the user."
msgstr ""
"ບາດນີ້ລອງນຳວິທີຄິດນີ້ມາໃຊ້ກັບການຂຽນໂປຣແກຣມ. ສົມມຸດວ່າພວກເຮົາຕ້ອງການໂປຣແກຣມທີ່ບວກເລກສອງຕົວທີ່ຜູ້ໃຊ້ປ້"
"ອນເຂົ້າມາ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo brings all of these pieces together in one integrated solution. With powerful apps for course creation, sales, marketing, and student engagement, Odoo empowers you to deliver exceptional learning experiences while keeping\n"
"            administration efficient and scalable."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ລວມທຸກສິ່ງເຫຼົ່ານີ້ເຂົ້າໄວ້ໃນບ່ອນດຽວ. ດ້ວຍແອັບຯທີ່ມີປະສິດທິພາບສຳລັບການສ້າງຫຼັກສູດ, ການຂາຍ, ການຕະ"
"ຫຼາດ ແລະ ການສ້າງສ່ວນຮ່ວມກັບນັກຮຽນ, Odoo ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານມອບປະສົບການການຮຽນຮູ້ທີ່ດີເລີດ ພ້ອມທັງບໍລິຫານຈັດ"
"ການໄດ້ຢ່າງມີປະສິດທິພາບ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo.com/trial"
msgstr "Odoo.com/trial"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo’s flexibility doesn’t stop at eLearning. Expand your platform with "
"additional apps to cover the full spectrum of your operations:"
msgstr ""
"ຄວາມຢືດຢຸ່ນຂອງ Odoo ບໍ່ໄດ້ຢຸດຢູ່ພຽງແຕ່ eLearning. ທ່ານສາມາດຂະຫຍາຍແພລດຟອມຂອງທ່ານດ້ວຍແອັບຯເພີ່ມ"
"ເຕີມເພື່ອຄອບຄຸມການເຮັດວຽກທັງໝົດ:"

#. module: elearning_platform
