msgid "Simple, direct code is easier to understand and less error-prone."
msgstr ""
"ໂຄ້ດທີ່ງ່າຍດາຍ ແລະ ຕົງໄປຕົງມາ ຈະເຂົ້າໃຈໄດ້ງ່າຍກວ່າ ແລະ ເກີດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດໜ້ອຍກວ່າ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.ir_ui_view_3213
msgid ""
"Skill up and have an impact! Your business career starts here.<br/>Time to "
"start a course."
msgstr ""
"ເພີ່ມທັກສະ ແລະ ສ້າງຜົນກະທົບ! ອະນາຄົດທຸລະກິດຂອງທ່ານເລີ່ມຕົ້ນທີ່ນີ້.<br/>ໄດ້ເວລາເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຫຼັກສູດແລ້ວ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid "Social Marketing Documentation"
msgstr "ເອກະສານການຕະຫຼາດຜ່ານໂຊຊຽວ"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Social Marketing integrates platforms like YouTube, LinkedIn, and Instagram "
"into your communication strategy. Schedule posts, track engagement, and stay"
" in touch with your community to boost brand presence and student loyalty."
msgstr ""
"ການຕະຫຼາດຜ່ານໂຊຊຽວລວມເອົາແພລດຟອມຕ່າງໆ ເຊັ່ນ: YouTube, LinkedIn ແລະ Instagram ເຂົ້າໃນກົ"
"ນລະຍຸດການສື່ສານຂອງທ່ານ. ວາງແຜນການໂພສ, ຕິດຕາມສ່ວນຮ່ວມ ແລະ ສື່ສານກັບຊຸມຊົນຂອງທ່ານເພື່ອສ້າງຊື່ສຽງ "
"ແລະ ຄວາມພັກດີຂອງນັກຮຽນ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_42
msgid "Spread 1 tablespoon of butter on the bread."
msgstr "ທາເບີ 1 ບ່ວງແກງໃສ່ເຂົ້າຈີ່."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid "Stand the bookshelf upright."
msgstr "ຕັ້ງຕູ້ປຶ້ມໃຫ້ຊື່."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.ir_ui_view_3213
msgid "Start your online course today!"
msgstr "ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຫຼັກສູດອອນລາຍຂອງທ່ານໃນມື້ນີ້!"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_52
msgid "Step 1: Plan the Steps"
msgstr "ຂັ້ນຕອນທີ 1: ວາງແຜນຂັ້ນຕອນ"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_52
msgid "Step 2: Write the Code"
msgstr "ຂັ້ນຕອນທີ 2: ຂຽນໂຄ້ດ"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_52
msgid "Step 3: How It Works"
msgstr "ຂັ້ນຕອນທີ 3: ມັນເຮັດວຽກແນວໃດ"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_52
msgid "Step 4: Extend the Game (Optional Challenges)"
msgstr "ຂັ້ນຕອນທີ 4: ຕໍ່ຍອດເກມ (ສິ່ງທ້າທາຍເພີ່ມເຕີມ)"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:elearning_platform.product_template_73
msgid ""
"Step into the world of technology with <em>Intro to IT</em>, a beginner-"
"friendly course designed to demystify computers, networks, and digital "
"systems. From hardware basics and operating systems to software applications"
" and online security, you’ll gain the essential knowledge to feel confident "
"in today’s tech-driven world."
msgstr ""
"ກ້າວເຂົ້າສູ່ໂລກແຫ່ງເຕັກໂນໂລຊີກັບ <em>ພື້ນຖານໄອທີ</em>, ຫຼັກສູດສຳລັບຜູ້ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນທີ່ອອກແບບມາເພື່ອເຮັດໃຫ້ເລື່ອ"
"ງຄອມພິວເຕີ, ເຄືອຂ່າຍ ແລະ ລະບົບດີຈີຕອນເປັນເລື່ອງງ່າຍ. ຕັ້ງແຕ່ພື້ນຖານຮາດແວ ແລະ ລະບົບປະຕິບັດການ ໄປຈົ"
"ນຮອດຊອບແວແອັບພລິເຄຊັນ ແລະ ຄວາມປອດໄພອອນລາຍ, ທ່ານຈະໄດ້ຮັບຄວາມຮູ້ທີ່ຈຳເປັນເພື່ອຄວາມໝັ້ນໃຈໃນໂລກຍຸ"
"ກເຕັກໂນໂລຊີ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_51
msgid ""
"Sticking to a logical order (imports at the top, functions grouped "
"together)."
msgstr ""
"ຮັກສາລຳດັບທີ່ມີເຫດຜົນ (ເຊັ່ນ: ການນຳເຂົ້າ library ໄວ້ທາງເທິງ, ຈັດກຸ່ມຟັງຊັນໄວ້ນຳກັນ)."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid "Store that number in a variable."
msgstr "ເກັບຕົວເລກນັ້ນໄວ້ໃນຕົວປ່ຽນ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid "Store the result in another variable."
msgstr "ເກັບຜົນຮັບໄວ້ໃນຕົວປ່ຽນອີກອັນໜຶ່ງ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid "Strategies for Breaking Down Problems"
msgstr "ກົນລະຍຸດໃນການແຍກບັນຫາ"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model:product.tag,name:elearning_platform.product_tag_3
msgid "Subscription Plan"
msgstr "ແຜນການສະໝັກສະມາຊິກ"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_42
msgid "Take 2 slices of bread."
msgstr "ເອົາເຂົ້າຈີ່ 2 ແຜ່ນ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid "Take board A and attach it to board B."
msgstr "ເອົາແຜ່ນໄມ້ A ມາຕິດໃສ່ແຜ່ນໄມ້ B."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid "Take out a slice of bread."
msgstr "ເອົາເຂົ້າຈີ່ອອກມາແຜ່ນໜຶ່ງ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_42
msgid "Take this simple example in Python:"
msgstr "ເບິ່ງຕົວຢ່າງງ່າຍໆນີ້ໃນພາສາ Python:"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid ""
"That’s exactly what programming is — taking a large, intimidating goal "
"(<em>a complete bookshelf</em>) and dividing it into smaller, executable "
"actions (<em>attach this board, insert this screw</em>)."
msgstr ""
"ນັ້ນຄືສິ່ງທີ່ການຂຽນໂປຣແກຣມເປັນ — ການເອົາເປົ້າໝາຍໃຫຍ່ໆ (<em>ຕູ້ປຶ້ມທີ່ສຳເລັດຮູບ</em>) ແລ້ວແບ່ງມັນອອກເ"
"ປັນຂັ້ນຕອນນ້ອຍໆທີ່ເຮັດໄດ້ (<em>ຕິດແຜ່ນໄມ້ນີ້, ໃສ່ສະກູອັນນີ້</em>)."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid ""
"That’s why programmers learn to decompose big, messy tasks into smaller, "
"manageable instructions. This approach is called <strong>algorithmic "
"thinking</strong>. An algorithm is simply a sequence of steps that describe "
"how to solve a problem."
msgstr ""
"ນັ້ນຄືເຫດຜົນທີ່ນັກຂຽນໂປຣແກຣມຮຽນຮູ້ທີ່ຈະແຍກວຽກໃຫຍ່ໆທີ່ວຸ້ນວາຍ ໃຫ້ກາຍເປັນຄຳສັ່ງນ້ອຍໆທີ່ຈັດການໄດ້. ວິທີນີ້ເອີ້ນ"
"ວ່າ <strong>ການຄິດແບບອັນກໍຣິທຶມ</strong>. ອັນກໍຣິທຶມກໍ່ຄືລຳດັບຂອງຂັ້ນຕອນທີ່ບອກວິທີແກ້ໄຂບັນຫານັ້ນເອງ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_52
msgid ""
"The <strong>while loop</strong> keeps running until the player guesses "
"correctly."
msgstr ""
"<strong>while loop</strong> ຈະເຮັດວຽກຕໍ່ໄປເລື້ອຍໆຈົນກວ່ານັກຫຼິ້ນຈະທາຍຖືກ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_52
msgid "The Goal"
msgstr "ເປົ້າໝາຍ"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_51
msgid ""
"The best code is often the simplest solution that works. Avoid “clever "
"hacks” that confuse future readers."
msgstr ""
"ໂໂຄ້ດທີ່ດີທີ່ສຸດມັກຈະເປັນວິທີທີ່ງ່າຍທີ່ສຸດທີ່ເຮັດວຽກໄດ້. ຫຼີກເວັ້ນການໃຊ້ “ເຕັກນິກພິເສດ” ທີ່ອາດຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ຜູ້ອ່ານໃນອ"
"ະນາຄົດສັບສົນ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_51
msgid "The clean version:"
msgstr "ເວີຊັນທີ່ສະອາດ:"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_52
msgid "The computer chooses a random number."
msgstr "ຄອມພິວເຕີສຸ່ມຕົວເລກຂຶ້ນມາ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The eLearning app is the foundation of your digital training. It allows you to create courses with multimedia content such as videos, articles, or downloadable materials. Add interactive elements like quizzes, certificates, and\n"
"            gamification to boost learner motivation. Assign course managers to keep content up to date and responsive to feedback."
msgstr ""
"ແອັບຯ eLearning ແມ່ນພື້ນຖານຂອງການຝຶກອົບຮົມດີຈີຕອນຂອງທ່ານ. ມັນຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານສ້າງຫຼັກສູດທີ່ມີເນື້ອຫາຫຼາກຫຼາ"
"ຍ ເຊັ່ນ: ວິດີໂອ, ບົດຄວາມ ຫຼື ເອກະສານທີ່ດາວໂຫຼດໄດ້. ເພີ່ມອົງປະກອບໂຕ້ຕອບ ເຊັ່ນ: ບົດທົດສອບ, ໃບຢັ້ງຢືນ "
"ແລະ ລະບົບເກມເພື່ອສ້າງແຮງຈູງໃຈ. ມອບໝາຍຜູ້ຈັດການຫຼັກສູດເພື່ອປັບປຸງເນື້ອຫາໃຫ້ທັນສະໄໝຢູ່ສະເໝີ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_52
msgid ""
"The number guessing game is more than just fun — it’s a practical way to see"
" how variables, loops, conditions, and input/output all come together to "
"form a working program. By experimenting with extensions, you’ll also "
"practice adapting and improving code, which is the true skill of "
"programming."
msgstr ""
"ເກມທາຍຕົວເລກເປັນຫຼາຍກວ່າຄວາມມ່ວນ — ມັນແມ່ນວິທີທີ່ນຳໃຊ້ໄດ້ຈິງເພື່ອໃຫ້ເຫັນວ່າຕົວປ່ຽນ, ລູບ, ເງື່ອນໄຂ ແລ"
"ະ ຂໍ້ມູນຂາເຂົ້າ/ຂາອອກ ເຮັດວຽກຮ່ວມກັນແນວໃດຈົນກາຍເປັນໂປຣແກຣມ. ໂດຍການທົດລອງປັບປຸງເກມ, ທ່ານກໍ່ຈະໄ"
"ດ້ຝຶກຝົນການປັບປ່ຽນ ແລະ ພັດທະນາໂຄ້ດ ເຊິ່ງເປັນທັກສະທີ່ແທ້ຈິງຂອງການຂຽນໂປຣແກຣມ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_41
msgid ""
"The output here is <strong>8</strong>, but notice how detailed the "
"instructions are. Programming is less about the complexity of math and more "
"about clarity and logic. The role of the programmer is to think carefully "
"about problems, break them into smaller steps, and express those steps in "
"code."
msgstr ""
"ຜົນຮັບຢູ່ນີ້ແມ່ນ <strong>8</strong>, ແຕ່ໃຫ້ສັງເກດເບິ່ງລາຍລະອຽດຂອງຄຳສັ່ງ. ການຂຽນໂປຣແກຣມບໍ່ແມ່ນເ"
"ລື່ອງຄວາມຊັບຊ້ອນຂອງຄະນິດສາດ, ແຕ່ແມ່ນເລື່ອງຄວາມຊັດເຈນ ແລະ ຕັກກະ. ບົດບາດຂອງນັກຂຽນໂປຣແກຣມແມ່ນກ"
"ານຄິດກ່ຽວກັບບັນຫາຢ່າງລະອຽດ, ແຍກອອກເປັນຂັ້ນຕອນນ້ອຍໆ ແລະ ປ່ຽນຂັ້ນຕອນເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນໃຫ້ເປັນໂຄ້ດ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_52
msgid "The player tries to guess it."
msgstr "ນັກຫຼິ້ນພະຍາຍາມທາຍຕົວເລກນັ້ນ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_52
msgid ""
"The program gives hints (“too high” or “too low”) until the player guesses "
"correctly."
msgstr ""
"ໂປຣແກຣມຈະໃຫ້ຄຳແນະນຳ (“ສູງເກີນໄປ” ຫຼື “ຕ່ຳເກີນໄປ”) ຈົນກວ່ານັກຫຼິ້ນຈະທາຍຖືກ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_43
msgid ""
"There are hundreds of programming languages, but a handful dominate the "
"industry. Each has its strengths, weaknesses, and communities built around "
"them. Here’s a closer look:"
msgstr ""
"ມີພາສາການຂຽນໂປຣແກຣມເປັນຮ້ອຍໆພາສາ, ແຕ່ມີພຽງບໍ່ເທົ່າໃດພາສາທີ່ຄອບຄອງອຸດສາຫະກຳນີ້. ແຕ່ລະພາສາມີຈຸດແ"
"ຂງ, ຈຸດອ່ອນ ແລະ ຊຸມຊົນທີ່ແຕກຕ່າງກັນ. ມາເບິ່ງລາຍລະອຽດກັນເລີຍ:"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,description:elearning_platform.slide_slide_43
msgid ""
"There are many programming languages, each designed for different kinds of "
"tasks."
msgstr ""
"ມີພາສາການຂຽນໂປຣແກຣມຫຼາຍພາສາ, ເຊິ່ງແຕ່ລະພາສາຖືກອອກແບບມາສຳລັບວຽກທີ່ແຕກຕ່າງກັນ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_51
msgid ""
"Think of clean code like good handwriting: anyone can scribble a note, but "
"if you want others to read it quickly and without confusion, neatness "
"matters."
msgstr ""
"ລອງນຶກວ່າໂຄ້ດທີ່ສະອາດຄືກັບລາຍມືທີ່ງາມ: ໃຜໆກໍ່ສາມາດຂຽນໝາຍເຫດໄດ້, ແຕ່ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການໃຫ້ຄົນອື່ນອ່ານໄດ້ໄ"
"ວ ແລະ ບໍ່ສັບສົນ, ຄວາມເປັນລະບຽບຮຽບຮ້ອຍແມ່ນສິ່ງສຳຄັນ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_51
msgid "Think of comments as a guidebook for anyone reading your code."
msgstr ""
"ລອງນຶກວ່າຄຳອະທິບາຍ (comments) ຄືກັບປຶ້ມຄູ່ມືສຳລັບທຸກຄົນທີ່ມາອ່ານໂຄ້ດຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid ""
"Think of it like following a recipe. Instead of just saying, <em>“Bake a "
"cake,”</em> the recipe tells you:"
msgstr ""
"ລອງນຶກເບິ່ງວ່າຄືກັບການເຮັດຕາມສູດອາຫານ. ແທນທີ່ຈະບອກແຕ່ <em>“ອົບເຄັກ,”</em> ແຕ່ສູດອາຫານຈະບອກທ່າ"
"ນວ່າ:"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_51
msgid ""
"Think of messy code as a recipe scribbled on a napkin: hard to read, full of"
" shorthand, maybe even missing steps. You <em>could</em> cook from it, but "
"it’s stressful. Clean code is like a proper recipe in a cookbook: clear "
"titles, numbered steps, and consistent formatting. Anyone can follow it, not"
" just the person who wrote it."
msgstr ""
"ລອງນຶກວ່າໂຄ້ດທີ່ບໍ່ເປັນລະບຽບຄືກັບສູດອາຫານທີ່ຂຽນໄວ້ໃນເຈ້ຍເຊັດປາກ: ອ່ານຍາກ, ເຕັມໄປດ້ວຍຕົວຫຍໍ້ ແລະ ອາດ"
"ຈະຂາດບາງຂັ້ນຕອນ. ທ່ານ <em>ອາດຈະ</em> ແຕ່ງກິນຕາມນັ້ນໄດ້, ແຕ່ມັນກໍ່ໜ້າເບື່ອ. ສ່ວນໂຄ້ດທີ່ສະອາດແມ່ນຄືກັ"
"ບສູດອາຫານໃນປຶ້ມແຕ່ງກິນທີ່ດີ: ມີຊື່ຊັດເຈນ, ມີຕົວເລກລຳດັບຂັ້ນຕອນ ແລະ ມີຮູບແບບທີ່ຄົງທີ່. ໃຜໆກໍ່ສາມາດເຮັດຕາມ"
"ໄດ້, ບໍ່ແມ່ນແຕ່ຄົນທີ່ຂຽນມັນຂຶ້ນມາ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_42
msgid ""
"This is why programming often feels like giving hyper-detailed instructions."
" The better you learn to translate human goals into structured steps, the "
"more powerful your programs become."
msgstr ""
"ນີ້ຄືເຫດຜົນທີ່ການຂຽນໂປຣແກຣມມັກຈະຮູ້ສຶກຄືກັບການໃຫ້ຄຳສັ່ງທີ່ມີລາຍລະອຽດສູງ. ຍິ່ງທ່ານຮຽນຮູ້ທີ່ຈະແປເປົ້າໝາຍຂອງ"
"ມະນຸດໃຫ້ເປັນຂັ້ນຕອນທີ່ມີໂຄງສ້າງໄດ້ດີສຳໃດ, ໂປຣແກຣມຂອງທ່ານກໍ່ຈະມີປະສິດທິພາບຫຼາຍຂຶ້ນສຳນັ້ນ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_51
msgid ""
"This makes your code shorter, easier to change, and less prone to mistakes."
msgstr ""
"ສິ່ງນີ້ຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ໂຄ້ດຂອງທ່ານສັ້ນລົງ, ປ່ຽນແປງໄດ້ງ່າຍຂຶ້ນ ແລະ ເກີດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດໜ້ອຍລົງ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_52
msgid "This simple game teaches you how to:"
msgstr "ເກມງ່າຍໆນີ້ຈະສອນໃຫ້ທ່ານຮູ້ວິທີ:"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_42
msgid "To illustrate how precise computers are, imagine telling a human:"
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອໃຫ້ເຫັນພາບວ່າຄອມພິວເຕີເຮັດວຽກໄດ້ຊັດເຈນສຳໃດ, ລອງນຶກພາບເບິ່ງວ່າຖ້າທ່ານບອກຄົນ:"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_42
msgid ""
"To you, it looks like a friendly, readable line of text. Behind the scenes, "
"Python translates this into thousands of binary instructions for the CPU: "
"storing characters, sending signals to the operating system, and displaying "
"text on the screen. The programmer doesn’t have to think about those tiny "
"details—just about the logic they want to express."
msgstr ""
"ສຳລັບທ່ານ, ມັນເບິ່ງຄືວ່າມັນເປັນຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ອ່ານງ່າຍ. ແຕ່ເບື້ອງຫຼັງແລ້ວ, Python ຈະແປຂໍ້ຄວາມນີ້ໃຫ້ເປັນຄຳສັ່ງເລ"
"ກຖານສອງຫຼາຍພັນຄຳສັ່ງສຳລັບ CPU: ເຊັ່ນການເກັບຕົວອັກສອນ, ການສົ່ງສັນຍານຫາລະບົບປະຕິບັດການ ແລະ ການສ"
"ະແດງຂໍ້ຄວາມເທິງໜ້າຈໍ. ນັກຂຽນໂປຣແກຣມບໍ່ຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງຄິດເຖິງລາຍລະອຽດນ້ອຍໆເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນ — ພຽງແຕ່ຄິດເຖິງຕັກກະ"
"ທີ່ຕ້ອງການສະແດງອອກກໍ່ພໍ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.ir_ui_view_3213
msgid "Toggle navigation"
msgstr "ປ່ຽນການນຳທາງ"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model:product.template,description_sale:elearning_platform.product_template_67
msgid "Turn your ideas into beautiful, functional furniture."
msgstr "ປ່ຽນຄວາມຄິດຂອງທ່ານໃຫ້ເປັນເຟີນີເຈີທີ່ສວຍງາມ ແລະ ໃຊ້ງານໄດ້ດີ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:elearning_platform.product_template_67
msgid "Unlimited lifetime access to all lessons and resources"
msgstr "ເຂົ້າເຖິງທຸກບົດຮຽນ ແລະ ແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນໄດ້ບໍ່ຈຳກັດຕະຫຼອດຊີວິດ"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_52
msgid "Use loops to repeat until a condition is met."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ລູບ (loops) ເພື່ອເຮັດຊ້ຳຈົນກວ່າຈະກົງກັບເງື່ອນໄຂ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_51
msgid "Uses descriptive variable names."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ຊື່ຕົວປ່ຽນທີ່ອະທິບາຍຄວາມໝາຍໄດ້ຊັດເຈນ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_51
msgid "Using spacing to make code visually clear."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ການຍະຫວ່າງເພື່ອໃຫ້ໂຄ້ດເບິ່ງແລ້ວຊັດເຈນ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_51
msgid "Using the same naming style (e.g., snake_case in Python)."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ຮູບແບບການຕັ້ງຊື່ແບບດຽວກັນ (ເຊັ່ນ: snake_case ໃນ Python)."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_51
msgid "Variable and function names should describe what they store or do."
msgstr "ຊື່ຕົວປ່ຽນ ແລະ ຟັງຊັນຄວນອະທິບາຍວ່າພວກມັນເກັບຫຍັງ ຫຼື ເຮັດຫຍັງ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model:slide.slide,name:elearning_platform.slide_slide_45
msgid "Variables & Data Types"
msgstr "ຕົວປ່ຽນ ແລະ ຊະນິດຂອງຂໍ້ມູນ"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid "Verify the PIN."
msgstr "ກວດສອບລະຫັດ PIN."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.ir_ui_view_3213
msgid "View"
msgstr "ເບິ່ງ"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.ir_ui_view_3213
msgid "View all"
msgstr "ເບິ່ງທັງໝົດ"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid "Wait for the user to type a number."
msgstr "ລໍຖ້າໃຫ້ຜູ້ໃຊ້ປ້ອນຕົວເລກ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid "Wait until the bread pops up."
msgstr "ລໍຖ້າຈົນກວ່າເຂົ້າຈີ່ຈະເດັ້ງຂຶ້ນມາ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid "Walk to the cupboard."
msgstr "ຍ່າງໄປທີ່ຕູ້."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid "Walk to the toaster."
msgstr "ຍ່າງໄປທີ່ຈັກປີ້ງເຂົ້າຈີ່."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:elearning_platform.homepage
msgid ""
"We believe the best way to master new skills is through hands-on practice. "
"Our courses combine clear explanations with real-world exercises so you can "
"immediately apply what you learn."
msgstr ""
"ພວກເຮົາເຊື່ອວ່າວິທີທີ່ດີທີ່ສຸດໃນການຮຽນຮູ້ທັກສະໃໝ່ແມ່ນຜ່ານການລົງມືເຮັດຕົວຈິງ. ຫຼັກສູດຂອງພວກເຮົາລວມເອົາຄຳອະ"
"ທິບາຍທີ່ຊັດເຈນເຂົ້າກັບບົດຝຶກຫັດຕົວຈິງ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ທ່ານສາມາດນຳໃຊ້ສິ່ງທີ່ຮຽນຮູ້ໄດ້ທັນທີ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_52
msgid ""
"Welcome to the Number Guessing Game!\n"
"Enter your guess (1–20): 10\n"
"Too low, try again!\n"
"Enter your guess (1–20): 15\n"
"Too high, try again!\n"
"Enter your guess (1–20): 12\n"
"🎉 Congratulations! You guessed the number!"
msgstr ""
"ຍິນດີຕ້ອນຮັບເຂົ້າສູ່ເກມທາຍຕົວເລກ!\n"
"ປ້ອນຕົວເລກທີ່ທ່ານທາຍ (1–20): 10\n"
"ຕ່ຳເກີນໄປ, ລອງໃໝ່ອີກຄັ້ງ!\n"
"ປ້ອນຕົວເລກທີ່ທ່ານທາຍ (1–20): 15\n"
"ສູງເກີນໄປ, ລອງໃໝ່ອີກຄັ້ງ!\n"
"ປ້ອນຕົວເລກທີ່ທ່ານທາຍ (1–20): 12\n"
"🎉 ຂໍສະແດງຄວາມຍິນດີ! ທ່ານທາຍຖືກແລ້ວ!"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid "What information does the program need to start?"
msgstr "ໂປຣແກຣມຕ້ອງການຂໍ້ມູນໃດແດ່ເພື່ອເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ?"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model:slide.slide,name:elearning_platform.slide_slide_41
msgid "What is Programming?"
msgstr "ການຂຽນໂປຣແກຣມແມ່ນຫຍັງ?"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid "What should it produce at the end?"
msgstr "ມັນຄວນຈະໃຫ້ຜົນຮັບຫຍັງໃນຕອນທ້າຍ?"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_50
msgid ""
"When facing a bigger programming challenge, here are some strategies to "
"decompose it:"
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອພົບກັບສິ່ງທ້າທາຍໃຫຍ່ໆໃນການຂຽນໂປຣແກຣມ, ນີ້ແມ່ນບາງກົນລະຍຸດເພື່ອແຍກບັນຫານັ້ນ:"

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_51
msgid ""
"When names are descriptive, you can often understand the code without extra "
"comments."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອຊື່ມີຄວາມໝາຍຊັດເຈນ, ທ່ານມັກຈະເຂົ້າໃຈໂຄ້ດໄດ້ໂດຍບໍ່ຕ້ອງມີຄຳອະທິບາຍເພີ່ມເຕີມ."

#. module: elearning_platform
#: model_terms:slide.slide,html_content:elearning_platform.slide_slide_42
msgid ""
"When you write code in a language like Python or Java, it doesn’t stay in "
"that human-readable form. Instead, it’s passed through a "
"<strong>compiler</strong> or <strong>interpreter</strong>, which translates "
"the instructions into machine code that the computer’s processor can "
"understand."
msgstr ""
